flowchart TD
    LoginPage[GET /login] --> Submit[POST /login]
    Submit --> Lookup[Find user by email]
    Lookup --> CheckPassword{Password hash valid}
    CheckPassword -- No --> LoginError[Flash error and render login]
    CheckPassword -- Yes --> ActiveCheck{User active}
    ActiveCheck -- No --> LoginError
    ActiveCheck -- Yes --> Session[Flask-Login session cookie]
    Session --> ProfileGuard{Profile setup complete}
    ProfileGuard -- No --> ProfileSetup[/profile/setup]
    ProfileGuard -- Yes --> Dashboard[/dashboard]
    Dashboard --> RouteGuard{Route role check}
    RouteGuard -- Allowed --> Handler[Route handler]
    RouteGuard -- Denied --> Forbidden[403 or redirect]
    Handler --> ReadonlyGuard{Readonly auditor writing}
    ReadonlyGuard -- Yes --> Forbidden
    ReadonlyGuard -- No --> Response[Response]
